//r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2Fa-hongkong-les-fonctionnaires-denoncent-leur-propre-administration_5496228_3210.html&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=46e01422\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lemonde.fr/international/article/2019/08/03/a-hongkong-les-fonctionnaires-denoncent-leur-propre-administration_5496228_3210.html</a><br />\n<br />\nLe Monde知名度都幾高 希望國際聽到我地嘅聲音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"85之後<br />\n<br />\n[參考波蘭成功例子既最佳戰術] 完全剋制政府冷處理 - 罷買 <br />\n一個最有效既長期戰術, 麻煩入去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n1. 週期性罷買係相當可行既一個戰術, 因為更能夠令普通人適應<br />\n2. 罷買影響力可以好大<br />\n3. 政府用冷處理戰術,打算拖至9月,而罷買係開學之後一樣可以實行,可以向社會施加壓力既最好方法<br />\n4. 罷買比遊行, 三罷, 更能夠說服中立派/和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9cc74bd1c80077897bb9535c2613a7cc8829ea65","tid":1400454,"uid":105657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dd0c12f334687d050a8f761d5e7feda70568ce9","tid":1400454,"uid":105657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"推x1"},{"pid":"17c7849dab298f03988ada6b1544f4a33a4b75a1","tid":1400454,"uid":105657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"推x2"},{"pid":"94b5112a475a5f78448dc374a6e522959cc14a73","tid":1400454,"uid":105657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"推x3"},{"pid":"952b06ae13f3934c972353eca698ffac0b10ce4f","tid":1400454,"uid":105657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"推x4"},{"pid":"7c1a14584f08b25ea87b4348319f79fe56ed400e","tid":1400454,"uid":105657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"推x5"},{"pid":"b8156d2680c99f7e65d6855fd3599d5d97217232","tid":1400454,"uid":280673,"li